_pdbx_molecule_features.details   
;CYCLOSPORIN IS A CYCLIC UNDECAPEPTIDE.                
 CYCLIZATION IS ACHIEVED BY LINKING THE N- AND         
 THE C- TERMINI.                                       
 THE CYCLOSPORIN WAS MODIFIED AT POSITION 5 TO BE      
